scene.message:
Nanjo: Speaking of which,{nl}
what about the hospital?{nl}
Weren't we headed there{nl}
for checkups?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, {ctl0f:1},{nl}
this guy's being a pain —{nl}
come on, back me up here.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Mark's out there{nl}
picking fights again...{nl}
What's his problem?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Shouldn't they just{nl}
tear down buildings no one{nl}
uses? They become hangouts{nl}
for delinquents...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Shut up! That's{nl}
exactly my point — they turn{nl}
into delinquent hangouts.{nl}
Give me a break.{waitkey}{ret}
